<main>
    <div class="position-relative overflow-hidden p-3 p-md-5 m-md-3 text-center bg-dark text-light rounded">
        <div class="col-md-5 p-lg-5 mx-auto my-5">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-normal">Discover a New Way of Learning with Dave.</h1>
            <p class="lead fw-normal">Experience the Future of Personal Education. Dive into a World of Boundless Knowledge with Dave - Your AI Assistant, Tailored to Make Learning Effortless and Exciting.</p>
            <div class="image">
                <div class="floppy">
                    <div class="floppyDisk"></div>
                    <div class="floppyLabel"></div>
                    <div class="floppySlide animate"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
        <div class="feature col">
            <div class="feature-icon bg-primary bg-gradient">
                <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#collection"></use></svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Google Calendar Support</h2>
            <p>Our platform is currently undergoing development for Google Calendar integration feature. This function aims to open doors for the AI to manifest functionality akin to a personal assistant, such as scheduling and notifying important appointments. It is a step towards making your everyday task management hassle-free and ensuring you never miss a deadline.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature col">
            <div class="feature-icon bg-primary bg-gradient">
                <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#people-circle"></use></svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Personal Knowledge base</h2>
            <p>We recognize the value of well-organized, accessible personal notes in enhancing productivity. As such, we are working on a feature to integrate a personal journal into our system. This tool will empower you to record your thoughts, keep track of ideas, and reference them whenever you need. Our goal is to create a digital brain for you, where knowledge is never out of reach.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature col">
            <div class="feature-icon bg-primary bg-gradient">
                <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#toggles2"></use></svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Learning Assistant</h2>
            <p>Dave aims to empower individual learning and exploration. With Dave, you will be able to tap into a vast pool of knowledge across multiple disciplines efficiently. You can save your favorite templates of information for future reference, fostering continuous learning. We are working with passion to make Dave your go-to for academic and professional growth.</p>
        </div>

    </div>


